games.comment: Matthew Stafford tossed 2 picks - 1 late over the middle - and the Lions forgot how to tackle on an Adrian Peterson 27-yard touchdown run.

Matthew Stafford's strip-sack didn't help matters. However, Stafford was able to bounce back with a terrific performance to lead Detroit to victory.
